# Local logo PNGs — regenerate with `pnpm ingest`. In prod these live on R2/CDN
# (cdn.defitriangle.xyz/logos/...), so the local tree is only the no-creds fallback.
apps/web/public/logos/
# NOTE: assets.json (the manifest) IS committed — it's the deployed site's data
# source until Supabase lands. Logo image URLs in it point at the CDN.

